body:
Adds an explicit variant `tests` which can be one of `(none, tests, benchmarks)`. Resolves issue with current package.py whereby ENABLE_BENCHMARKS can be On when ENABLE_TESTS is Off, which is a no-go.

Fixes https://github.com/spack/spack/issues/17948

@cyrush @adrienbernede @rblake @adamjstewart
